abstract: He was told he would lose. In any other year, he probably would have. But 2001 was not any other year.
snippet: He was told he would lose. In any other year, he probably would have. But 2001 was not any other year.
lead_paragraph: Michael R. Bloomberg was not entirely picky.

abstract: Nearly four dozen nonprofits around the world are dedicated to removing photos and videos of child sexual abuse from the internet. It’s a daunting task.
snippet: Nearly four dozen nonprofits around the world are dedicated to removing photos and videos of child sexual abuse from the internet. It’s a daunting task.
lead_paragraph: Sexual predators have grown increasingly adept at using the internet to share and view child sexual abuse photos and videos. Some have computer-programming skills and have deployed sophisticated defenses against efforts to take them down.

abstract: Choosing a meaningful gift for a child — one they truly connect with and value — can be more challenging than it seems.
snippet: Choosing a meaningful gift for a child — one they truly connect with and value — can be more challenging than it seems.
lead_paragraph: When my 9-year-old daughter asked for a sewing machine last year, my instinct was to pick up a simple one for kids. It was inexpensive. It was easy. I could check it off my list and be done. But a good friend steered me away.
